column4: Changes current device id to the one specified in parameter. Merges user profile with new id  (if any) with old profile.
Returns the device id used by countly for this device

Set location parameters. If they are set before begin_session, they will be sent as part of it.  If they are set after, then they will be sent as a separate request.  If this is called after disabling location, it will enable it.
